---
layout: base.njk
title: Educational and Artistic Programs | C.A.P.I. Samaipata
description: Discover our artistic, pedagogical, and cultural programs designed for the community of Samaipata.
lang: en
translationKey: "programs"
---
<section class="programas-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="programas-hero__title">Our Programs</h1>
    <p class="programas-hero__text">
      We nurture talent and project futures through creative and humanistic education.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detalle-programas">
  <div class="container">
    <article class="programa-item">
      <div class="programa-item__image">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513364776144-60967b0f800f?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Art Workshops at CAPI"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="programa-item__info">
        <span class="categoria">Arts Department</span>
        <h2>Visual & Fine Arts</h2>
        <p>
          Following our vision of fostering creativity as a life tool, this program offers a dynamic and diverse space for both children and adults. We focus on enriching cultural life and strengthening the sense of belonging through free expression.
        </p>
        <ul class="lista-beneficios">
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Exploration of various techniques and materials
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Fostering conscious social participation
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Stimulating creativity and emotional well-being
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="programa-item programa-item--reverse">
      <div class="programa-item__image">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Comprehensive Pedagogical Support"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="programa-item__info">
        <span class="categoria">Educational Strengthening</span>
        <h2>Pedagogical Support</h2>
        <p>
          This program was created to address current issues such as school disinterest and the feeling of a lack of academic understanding. We provide accessible services to support teaching efforts and empower student autonomy in a motivating environment.
        </p>
        <ul class="lista-beneficios">
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Guidance for learning difficulties
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Development of motivation and study habits
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Personalized attention for children and youth
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="programa-item">
      <div class="programa-item__image">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511379938547-c1f69419868d?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Music Classes at CAPI"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="programa-item__info">
        <span class="categoria">Musical Training</span>
        <h2>Music & Singing</h2>
        <p>
          We feature an equipped music room for the training of new talents. Our strings program aims for each student not only to master an instrument but to find in music a refuge and a comprehensive form of communication.
        </p>
        <ul class="lista-beneficios">
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Specialized teaching in string instruments
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Practice and rehearsals in a professional room
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Development of discipline and artistic sensitivity
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="programa-item programa-item--reverse">
      <div class="programa-item__image">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529156069898-49953e39b3ac?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Cultural Engagement Samaipata"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="programa-item__info">
        <span class="categoria">Cultural Management</span>
        <h2>Culture & Community</h2>
        <p>
          As a reference center in Samaipata, we energize the area with cultural events, independent cinema, and theater. We seek to bridge the generational gap and create strong bonds between parents, teachers, and youth through art.
        </p>
        <ul class="lista-beneficios">
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Independent film cycles and theater
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Community festivals and concerts
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Meeting spaces for social dialogue
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="event-calendar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="calendar-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">{{ "Próximos Talleres y Encuentros" if lang == 'es' else "Upcoming Workshops and Gatherings" }}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="event-grid">
      {% for evento in eventos[lang] %}
      <article class="event-card">
        <div class="event-card__date">
          <span class="day">{{ evento.fecha | dateFilter('dd', lang) }}</span>
          <span class="month">{{ evento.fecha | dateFilter('LLL', lang) }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="event-card__content">
          <span class="category-tag">{{ evento.categoria }}</span>
          <h3>{{ evento.titulo }}</h3>
          <p class="time"><i class="far fa-clock"></i> {{ evento.hora }}</p>
          <p class="desc">{{ evento.descripcion }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event-card__footer">
          <a href="/{{ lang }}/contacto/" class="btn-link">{{ "Inscribirse" if lang == 'es' else "Register" }} →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
      <div class="event-grid">
  {% for evento in eventos[lang] %}
    {# ... tu código de tarjetas ... #}
  {% else %}
    <div class="no-events">
      <p>{{ "No hay eventos programados por el momento. ¡Vuelve pronto!" if lang == 'es' else "No events scheduled at the moment. Check back soon!" }}</p>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>